abstract: Aruna Dindane (born 26 November 1980) is an Ivorian footballer who is currently unattached and plays as a striker.He has 62 caps and 17 goals for the Ivory Coast since his debut in 2000, and has played at four Africa Cup of Nations and two FIFA World Cups.
